<view class="app-page dv"><view class="app-card app-card--glass dv-head"><view class="flex-row items-start justify-between"><view class="flex-col"><text class="dv-title">设备管理</text><text class="dv-sub">通过蓝牙连接设备，将每日监测数据同步到“身体数据”展示。</text></view><view class="{{['dv-chip', b]}}"><text class="dv-chip-text">{{a}}</text></view></view><view class="dv-kv"><view class="dv-kv-row"><text class="dv-k">已绑定设备</text><text class="dv-v">{{c}}</text></view><view class="dv-kv-row"><text class="dv-k">连接状态</text><text class="dv-v">{{d}}</text></view><view class="dv-kv-row"><text class="dv-k">最近同步</text><text class="dv-v">{{e}}</text></view></view><view class="dv-actions"><view class="btn-secondary dv-btn" bindtap="{{f}}">开启蓝牙</view><view class="btn-secondary dv-btn" bindtap="{{h}}">{{g}}</view><view bindtap="{{i}}" class="{{['btn-secondary', 'dv-btn', j]}}">断开</view><view class="btn-secondary dv-btn" bindtap="{{k}}">示例数据</view></view><text class="dv-hint">提示：首次使用请先开启手机蓝牙，并允许小程序使用蓝牙权限。</text></view><view class="dv-section flex-row items-center justify-between"><text class="app-section-title">附近设备</text><view class="dv-mini-link" bindtap="{{l}}"><text class="dv-mini-link-text">清空</text><text class="dv-arrow">›</text></view></view><view class="app-card dv-list"><view wx:if="{{m}}" class="dv-empty"><text class="dv-empty-text">未发现设备。点击“搜索设备”，或靠近设备后重试。</text></view><view wx:for="{{n}}" wx:for-item="d" wx:key="e" class="dv-item"><view class="flex-row items-center justify-between"><view class="flex-col"><text class="dv-item-name">{{d.a}}</text><text class="dv-item-id">{{d.b}}</text></view><view class="dv-item-right flex-row items-center"><text class="dv-rssi">{{d.c}}</text><view class="btn-primary dv-connect" bindtap="{{d.d}}"><text class="dv-connect-text">连接</text></view></view></view></view></view><view wx:if="{{o}}" class="dv-section flex-row items-center justify-between"><text class="app-section-title">数据接收</text><view class="dv-mini-link" bindtap="{{p}}"><text class="dv-mini-link-text">写入身体数据</text><text class="dv-arrow">›</text></view></view><view wx:if="{{q}}" class="app-card app-card--glass dv-rx"><view class="dv-rx-row"><text class="dv-k">自动同步</text><view class="flex-row items-center"><text class="dv-v" style="margin-right:12rpx">{{r}}</text><switch checked="{{s}}" bindchange="{{t}}"></switch></view></view><view class="dv-rx-row"><text class="dv-k">同步后端</text><view class="flex-row items-center"><text class="dv-v" style="margin-right:12rpx">{{v}}</text><switch checked="{{w}}" bindchange="{{x}}"></switch></view></view><view class="dv-rx-row"><text class="dv-k">后端同步</text><text class="dv-v">{{y}}</text></view><view class="dv-rx-row"><text class="dv-k">最近一条数据</text><text class="dv-v">{{z}}</text></view><view class="dv-rx-row"><text class="dv-k">解析结果</text><text class="dv-v">{{A}}</text></view><text class="dv-hint">说明：已支持 AT+DATA1=hr,o2,temp,bp,\r\n（bp 会映射为血压 mmHg）；同时也会尝试解析 JSON 或 key=value。</text></view><view class="dv-section flex-row items-center justify-between"><text class="app-section-title">手动补录</text><view class="dv-mini-link" bindtap="{{B}}"><text class="dv-mini-link-text">保存到身体数据</text><text class="dv-arrow">›</text></view></view><view class="app-card dv-form"><view class="dv-form-row"><text class="dv-label">血压</text><input class="dv-input" placeholder="如 132/85" value="{{C}}" bindinput="{{D}}"/><text class="dv-unit">mmHg</text></view><view class="dv-form-row"><text class="dv-label">心率</text><input class="dv-input" placeholder="如 68" type="number" value="{{E}}" bindinput="{{F}}"/><text class="dv-unit">次/分</text></view><view class="dv-form-row"><text class="dv-label">血糖</text><input class="dv-input" placeholder="如 6.8" type="digit" value="{{G}}" bindinput="{{H}}"/><text class="dv-unit">mmol/L</text></view><view class="dv-form-row"><text class="dv-label">测量类型</text><picker class="dv-picker" mode="selector" range="{{J}}" value="{{K}}" bindchange="{{L}}"><view class="dv-picker-text">{{I}}</view></picker></view><view class="dv-form-row"><text class="dv-label">体温</text><input class="dv-input" placeholder="如 36.6" type="digit" value="{{M}}" bindinput="{{N}}"/><text class="dv-unit">℃</text></view><view class="dv-form-row"><text class="dv-label">血氧</text><input class="dv-input" placeholder="如 97" type="number" value="{{O}}" bindinput="{{P}}"/><text class="dv-unit">%</text></view><view class="dv-form-row"><text class="dv-label">睡眠</text><input class="dv-input" placeholder="如 6.4" type="digit" value="{{Q}}" bindinput="{{R}}"/><text class="dv-unit">小时</text></view><view class="dv-form-tip"><text class="dv-form-tip-text">无法由设备获取的数据可在此补录，保存后会同步到“我的-身体数据”展示。</text></view></view></view>